    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey quick question, im taking sertraline for my mood but finals week is coming up and i feel super low and unmotivated. i was thinking about adding some st johns wort to help boost things up naturally since its herbal. is it okay to take them together or will that be an issue?",
