    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh man really? i didnt realize a herbal supplement could be that bad. i read online that st johns wort is just like a natural version of antidepressants so i thought it'd just add to what the sertraline is doing. are you sure it's actually dangerous? i feel like since it's just a plant it shouldn't mess with my meds that much.",
