      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what u mean about the serotonin but i'm already on a pretty low dose of sertraline so it shouldn't be that much of a problem right? like if i just take a small amount of the supplement it would probably just be a tiny boost. i really dont have time to wait for a doctor appointment before my exams start next week. can i just try a half dose and see how i feel?",
